review_title: Ok sure I will just start again
one_reviews_text: Horrible wouldnt let me save my game way to much in between each stage DO NOT BUY
review_feedback:
If you have not saved you game manually there is an autosave you can load too. 
Don't hesitate to contact me at support@deisim.com so I can guide you to load your autosave.

one_reviews_text:
Very good. there is enough contents to be enjoyed... I can't wait for more. Happy to see the dev coming with more soon. Keep going! it's definitively a unique Must Have.
Replayability, good mechanics, good views. Characters, buildings and objects well done.
This game is everyone anyone has ever wanted.

I love this game, I love building worlds and exploring more features. I just wish the terrain it self was more developed, life being able to make a volcano erupt or cause earthquakes or other features. I also would love there to be more control over the humans like changing the diplomacy or war.
review_feedback:
You will probably love what will come this year ;)
PS : You should try the flame button on the volcano
